## File Naming Conventions

- Inbox: ISO 8601 timestamp (`2026-01-24T10:30:00Z.md`)
- Weekly details: `YYYY-MM-DD-Www.md` (`2026-01-20-W04.md`)
- Monthly details: `YYYY-MM.md`
- Daily journal: `Resources/Journal/YYYY/MM/DD.md`

